### Delete Purchase
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/purchases/67f66c737ed7ddb60e54af70
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete All Purchases
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/purchases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
